            <p class="font-bold font-montserrat my-8">INSTANCES WHEN YOUR RELEVANT PERSONAL DATA IS PROCESSED BY OR MAY BE DISCLOSED TO THIRD PARTIES AND THE PURPOSE/S AND LEGAL BASIS FOR SUCH DISCLOSURES</p>
            <p class="text-[#3c4241] mb-3 lg:text-sm text-xs">La Salle University-Ozamiz, Inc., as its way of showing its gratitude to its benefactors, may occasionally publish the list of its donors. You may opt to tick the box that states you wish to make an anonymous donation; in which case, your name will not be included in the donor’s list that LSU may publish in its website and social media networks. Nonetheless, as stated above, LSU will require the processing of your personal information in order to comply with applicable laws and issuances.</p>
